  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The office is under siege by a horde of relentless zombies! Can you survive and protect your coworkers? Arm yourself, rally your colleagues, and strategize to eliminate the undead menace. It's up to you to save the day and restore order amidst the chaos. Will you rise to the challenge and become the hero your office needs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras/abcafd526ae96d51e05c3346f1de7d76.avif?t=1746615473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras_big/abcafd526ae96d51e05c3346f1de7d76.avif?t=1746615473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight through waves of zombies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle relentless zombie hordes and save uninfected workers by leading them to safety</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras/f3ef40b851e5c7e490d078f6d4c42798.avif?t=1746615473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras_big/f3ef40b851e5c7e490d078f6d4c42798.avif?t=1746615473 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit Coworkers to the Cause</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble a team of elite coworkers from four classes—Soldier, Medic, Engineer, and Athlete—to defend your workplace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras/64c59fb16321951d22f8362178c84321.avif?t=1746615473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras_big/64c59fb16321951d22f8362178c84321.avif?t=1746615473 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Up and Purchase Powerful Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your skills and those of your recruits, and uncover powerful weapons to face increasing waves of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras/cddc6e1abb38922a31d155a4d647bcad.avif?t=1746615473\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385870/extras_big/cddc6e1abb38922a31d155a4d647bcad.avif?t=1746615473 width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
